description: Dogs On Wheels was created to provide their customers with a friendly, & joyous out door food experience. They add a mix of fun to any scene with nostalgically retro, fifty's outdoor music & flare.  While you're there listening and enjoying the nostalgic tunes of Frank Sinatra, why not Travel your taste buds through each craving bite of  delicious toppings and ingredients inspired by some of the most popular Hot Dog traditions around.  Come relish the flavor and tell your friends and family why Dogs On Wheels Hot Dogs is your next destination to the newest crave of the south. Dogs On Wheels is sure to have your taste buds wheel'in back for more!!!
name: Dogs On Wheels
